  "text": "One psychologist [CITATION_1] commented that \"the existence of such unmotivated preferences remains a bit of experimental debris that tidy psychological theories have yet to sweep up\" (p. 358). The purpose of the present paper is to show that this stable and pandemic phenomenon of heptaphilia is far from being unmotivated.",
